data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED!!!  Price Lowered and Ready to Move.  Just in time to be in your new home before the holidays.  Inviting and warm best describes this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home.  Beautiful updated kitchen with granite, backsplash and nice cabinets.  Wood flooring throughout.  Take notice of the updated bathrooms. WOW! Tons of upgrades: New HVAC (compressor not replaced), New thermostat, New garage door and opener, New front door & storm door, New dishwasher, New blinds, New to Newer appliances (including washer & dryer) stays with property. Sewer line and water heater replaced in 2017. Extra larger back yard that can also be used for rear parking. This one is a WINNER! Ready to move right in.
